    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Android app with Google Map API v2]]></title>
    <link href="http://lynnequ.github.com/blog/2013/03/21/android-app-with-google-map-api-v2-tutorial/"/>
    <updated>2013-03-21T03:09:00-07:00</updated>
